  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "\n\nTime Switch: \nThis ability shifts the world between two states, changing
    the level layout in real time. Platforms will appear or disappear depending on
    the current timeline, allowing access to new paths and hidden routes. Use it
    strategically to navigate gaps and reach the end.\n\n\nSprint: \nSprinting increases
    your movement speed but drains your stamina. Once stamina is depleted, you must
    wait for it to recharge before sprinting again. Use sprinting to cross large
    gaps or escape tight situations, but don\u2019t overuse it.\n\n\nTimer: \nYou
    have a limited amount of time to complete the level. The timer continuously counts
    down\u2014if it reaches 0, the run ends in Game Over. Manage your movement and
    use abilities efficiently to reach the goal before time runs out."
