      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "\nSwitches:\n\nWill toggle state upon coming into contact with the player\n\nGreen
    = On\n\nWhen all switches are green, they will turn gold and activate a door\n\nMoving
    Platforms: Moving platforms are dynamic surfaces that travel along a set path\u2014adding
    timing and positioning challenges to basic platforming. They can carry the player
    across gaps and force precise jumps.\n\nBreakable Platforms: Platforms that disappear
    after a duration of time. The longer the player stands on this platform, the
    more red it becomes until it eventually disappears. Breakable Platforms respawn
    after 5 seconds.\n\nSpikes: Landing on spikes respawns the player to their most
    recent checkpoint.\n\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
